Package: banR
Type: Package
Title: R client for the BAN API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Joel Gombin, P.-A. Chevalier
Maintainer: Joel Gombin <joel.gombin@gmail.com>
Description: This packages is a client for the BAN API, which allows to (batch)
    geocode and reverse-geocode French adresses.
